Overland_Park.Dyke Branch:
Dyke Branch is a stream in the U.S. states of Kansas and Missouri. It is a tributary of Indian Creek. The headwaters are in eastern Kansas at 38°59′22″N 94°37′08″W and the confluence with Indian Creek is in Missouri at 38°57′08″N 94°34′40″W.
Dyke Branch has the name of the local Dyke family.
